# VEHICLE::CLOSE_BOMB_BAY_DOORS

## Summary
Drives the bomb bay doors to a close

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Command to close a bomb bay, this isn't setup like a normal door.
